## 概念代码

```c++
class CMemento 
{
public:
	CMemento(int state):m_state(state) {}
	int getState() {return m_state;}
private:
	int m_state;
};

class Originator
{
public:
	int getState() {return m_state;}
	void setState(int state) {m_state = state}
	CMemento* save2Memento()
	{
		return new CMemento(m_state);
	}
private:
	int m_state;
};

class CareTaker
{
private:
	list<CMemento*> m_list;
public:
	void save(CMemento* p)
	{
		m_list.add(p);
	}
};
```
